snippet.title: Basketball MAGNAVOX ODYSSEY (1973)
snippet.description:
Like many other magnavox games, this is the first Basketball videogame.
grab the simulator here: 
http://odysim.blogspot.com/
you can read the game manual here: 
https://ia801709.us.archive.org/33/items/Basketball_1972_Magnavox_US/Basketball_1972_Magnavox_US.pdf
 images from:
 https://www.uvlist.net/gamegallery-153642
You can visit the Odysim creator channel for more info about games and great new homebrew of the Magnavox Odyssey “odysim” here: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCvGTsHpp3R6eoiDjR1TxONw 
Music from BAD SNACKS…….Joy Ride.mp3 Visit her channel here: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBCI_QCAMe1hx8UNyvJlM_Q
